### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Objective
To forecast future carbon dioxide (CO‚ÇÇ) emissions and analyze the impact of renewable energy adoption on global emission reduction using AI and Machine Learning algorithms.  
This project uses real-world CO‚ÇÇ emission data collected from the **Global Carbon Budget (2024)**, published by **Our World in Data**.

