---

### 5Ô∏è‚É£ Dataset Description
This dataset provides **annual CO‚ÇÇ emissions** for multiple countries and regions from **1750 to 2023**.  
It is derived from the **Global Carbon Budget** and processed by **Our World in Data**.  
The data represents carbon dioxide emissions from fossil fuels and industrial sources (excluding land-use change).  
Values are measured in **tonnes of CO‚ÇÇ emitted per year**.

---

### 6Ô∏è‚É£ Target Variable
**Annual CO‚ÇÇ Emissions** (measured in tonnes)

---

### 7Ô∏è‚É£ Applications
- Forecasting future CO‚ÇÇ emission levels using ML models  
- Studying emission trends by country or continent  
- Supporting renewable energy and sustainability research  
- Helping policy development for carbon neutrality and climate change mitigation  

